What is Effort_count
Based on the API docs and the segment effort endpoint, an effort is one instance of one athlete completing the segment — so if you run the same segment 10 times, that counts as 10 efforts. effort_count is the total of all these completions across all athletes ever.

What is athlete_count
athlete_count is the total number of distinct athletes who have completed it at least once



